in which two people died. The communities have been rocked by gang-related violence over the years but there's no confirmation at this stage that Saturday's attack was carried out by gangsters. At least four people have been shot dead, and one injured in Tafelsig. eNCA reporter Ayesha Ismail was on the scene. Courtesy of #DStv403